rozesse und Entwicklungslinien zeichnet Benjamin Schulte anhand des Kyffhäuserbundes exemplarisch nach.  aUsing the example of the Kyffhäuserbund: The socially accepted image of a veteran of World War I largely resulted from intersubjective discourses of experience.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 4aDenkmal. 4aDeutsche Geschichte. 4aErinnerungskultur. 4aGeschichte des 20. Jahrhunderts. 4aGeschichtswissenschaft. 4aGesellschaft. 4aGewalt. 4aHeroismus. 4aKameradschaft. 4aKulturgeschichte. 4aKyffhäuserbund. 4aMythos. 4aNachkriegsgesellschaft. 4aNovemberrevolution. 4aPopulärkultur. 4aVereinswesen. 4aVersailles. 4aVeteranen. 4aWeimarer Republik. 4aZeitgeschichte. 7aHISTORY / Europe / Germany.2bisacsh  aClub.  aCompanionate.  aContemporary History.  aCultural History.  aGerman History.  aHeroism.  aHistory of the 20th Century.  aHistory.  aMemorial.  aMemory Culture.  aMyth.  aNovember Revolution.  aPopular Culture.  aPostwar Society.  aSociety.  aVersailles.  aVeterans.  aViolence.  aWeimar Republic.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2020 Part 2z978311069629508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2020z9783110704525oZDB-23-DEG40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839450895zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839450895423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839450895/original  a978-3-11-069629-5  DG Plus PP Package 2020 Part 2b2020  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DEGb2020  aZDB-23-DGGb2020